                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Arial Black' underline='true'>Key Insights</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Arial Black'>• Global COVID-19 cases peaked during 2021–2022, indicating highest healthcare demand.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Arial Black'>• Rapid vaccination rollout helped stabilize case growth post-2022.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Arial Black'>• A small number of countries account for a large share of total cases.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
